(44,1,"2018-10-19 17:47:08","2018-10-19 17:47:08","<style>\n/* IMAGINE */<br />\n.section-imagine {<br />\n    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)), url(../img/2.jpg);<br />\n    background-size: cover;<br />\n    background-position: center;<br />\n    background-attachment: fixed;<br />\n    height: auto;<br />\n}<br />\n.section-imagine h1 {<br />\n    color: #ffffff;<br />\n    font-weight: 700;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.hero-text-box {<br />\n    margin: auto;<br />\n    width: 60%;<br />\n    padding: 2%;<br />\n}<br />\n.yes, .no, .all {<br />\n    height: 20%;<br />\n    width: 100%;<br />\n    padding: 5px 20px;<br />\n    position: relative;<br />\n    margin: 30px 0;<br />\n    color: #ffffff;<br />\n    font-size: 10px;<br />\n}<br />\n.no {<br />\n    background-color: #EA813A;<br />\n    animation-name: slide;<br />\n    animation-duration: 2s;<br />\n}<br />\n.yes {<br />\n    background-color: #0096B2;<br />\n    animation-name: slide;<br />\n    animation-duration: 3s;<br />\n}<br />\n.all {<br />\n    background-color: #D1242C;<br />\n    animation-name: slide;<br />\n    animation-duration: 4s;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>@-webkit-keyframes slide {<br />\n    0%   {left:-100%;}<br />\n    100% {left:0;}<br />\n}</p>\n<p>@keyframes slide {<br />\n    0%   {left:-100%;}<br />\n    100% {left:0;}<br />\n}<br />\n.btn-custom-primary, .btn-custom-secondary {<br />\n    border-radius: 0;<br />\n    color: #ffffff;<br />\n    font-weight: 600;<br />\n}<br />\n.btn-custom-primary {<br />\n    background-color: transparent;<br />\n    border: 2px solid #64DD17;<br />\n    color: #64DD17;<br />\n}<br />\n.btn-custom-secondary {<br />\n    background-color: #558B2F;<br />\n    border: 2px solid #558B2F;<br />\n}<br />\n/* Opportunities */<br />\n.section-opportunities {<br />\n    background-color: #F5F5F5;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.chip {<br />\n    background-color: transparent;<br />\n    border: 2px solid #D28041;<br />\n    color: #D28041;<br />\n    font-size: 15px;<br />\n    margin: 5px;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.title {<br />\n    color: #1F94AE;<br />\n    font-size: 30px;<br />\n    font-weight: 700;<br />\n    border-bottom: 2px solid #009688;<br />\n    text-align: center;<br />\n    margin-bottom: 50px;<br />\n    padding: 20px 0;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>/* Center */<br />\n.section-center {<br />\n    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.9), rgba(0,0,0,0.9)), url(../img/5.jpg);<br />\n    background-size: cover;<br />\n    background-position: center;<br />\n    background-attachment: fixed;<br />\n    height: auto;<br />\n}<br />\n.section-center .container {<br />\n    background-color: #ffffff;<br />\n}<br />\n.section-center img {<br />\n    width: 50%;<br />\n}<br />\n.bullets {<br />\n    list-style: none;<br />\n    counter-reset: item;<br />\n    font-size: 20px;<br />\n    font-weight: 600;<br />\n}<br />\n.bullets li {<br />\n    counter-increment: item;<br />\n}<br />\n.bullets li:before {<br />\n    content: counter(item);<br />\n    color: #ffffff;<br />\n    background-color: #1F94AE;<br />\n    font-size: 120%;<br />\n    border-radius: 50%;<br />\n    display: inline-block;<br />\n    height: 55px;<br />\n    width: 55px;<br />\n    text-align: center;<br />\n    padding: 10px;<br />\n    margin-right: 25px;<br />\n    margin-bottom: 15px;<br />\n}<br />\n.concept-map { width: 100%; }<br />\n.media {<br />\n    margin-bottom: 25px;<br />\n}<br />\n.media img {<br />\n    width: 200px;<br />\n}<br />\n.section-workshops {<br />\n    background-color: #F5F5F5;<br />\n}<br />\n</style>\n<div class=\"section-imagine\">\n<div class=\"hero-text-box\">\n<h1>Imagine Building-Green</h1>\n<div class=\"no\">\n<h3><strong>No</strong>: Fossil Fuels: disconnect from Electric and Gas Utility</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"yes\">\n<h3><strong>Yes</strong>: Only Renewable Energy: Power, Heat, and Air Conditioning</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"all\">\n<h3><strong>All</strong>: Built at a Competitive Cost compared with Non-Renewable Energy Buildings.</h3>\n</div>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-custom-primary\">Get Started</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-custom-secondary\">Know More</button>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"section-opportunities\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h4 class=\"title\">Building-Green Opportunities</h4>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm\">\n<h5>Investors:</h5>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Sponsor STEM Scholarships</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Shares Ownership</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm\">\n<h5>Skills Development</h5>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Solar, Storage, Generation</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Green Fuels</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Lean Building Construction</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Business Plan Development</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm\">\n<h5>Your Own Small Business</h5>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Detailed Plans</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Financing</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Green Generator</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        On-going Step by Step Support</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm\">\n<h4 class=\"title\">Building-Green Facility Types</h4>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Technical Training Center</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        STEM Learning Labs</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Office Warehouse</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Fitness Center</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Workshop</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Office</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Retail</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        House</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Other</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm\">\n<h4 class=\"title\">Building-Green Concepts</h4>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Solar PV</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Solar Storage</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Green Generator</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Renewable Fuel Supply</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Integrated Controls</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Green Building Materials</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        HVAC Systems</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Video Conferencing</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        LEED Certifications</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section-center\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h4 class=\"title\">Demonstration Concepts</h4>\n<div id=\"carouselExampleIndicators\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n 	<li data-target=\"#carouselExampleIndicators\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n 	<li data-target=\"#carouselExampleIndicators\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\n<div class=\"carousel-item active\">\n                        <img class=\"d-block w-100\" src=\"resources/img/3.png\" alt=\"First slide\">\n<div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\">\n<h5>Renewable Energy Training Center</h5>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"carousel-item\">\n                        <img class=\"d-block w-100\" src=\"resources/img/4.jpg\" alt=\"Second slide\">\n<div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\">\n<h5>Energy Training Center</h5>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<a class=\"carousel-control-prev\" href=\"#carouselExampleIndicators\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n<span class=\"carousel-control-prev-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span>\n</a>\n<a class=\"carousel-control-next\" href=\"#carouselExampleIndicators\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n<span class=\"carousel-control-next-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n<span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm\">\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Single Axis Solar PV Systems</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Energy Storage Battery Systems</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Green Fuel CHP Systems</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Solar Water Heating</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        LEED Platinum Building</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Ultra Hi-Efficiency Education Bldg.</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Lean Building Construction</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Energy Data Analytics</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Business Case Development</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Leveraging Tax and Utility Incentives</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Energy Demand Management</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                        Remote Monitoring and Controls</div>\n<!--\n<ol class=\"bullets\">\n 	<li>Single Axis Solar PV Systems</li>\n 	<li>Energy Storage Battery Systems</li>\n 	<li>Green Fuel CHP Systems</li>\n 	<li>Solar Water Heating</li>\n 	<li>LEED Platinum Building</li>\n 	<li>Ultra Hi-Efficiency Education Bldg.</li>\n<!--\n<ol>\n 	<li>LED Lighting</li>\n 	<li>Solar Lighting</li>\n 	<li>Occupancy and Light Sensors</li>\n 	<li>Fresh Air Heat Exchangers</li>\n 	<li>Low Water Use Facilities</li>\n 	<li>Hi Efficiency HVAC</li>\n</ol>\n 	<li>Lean Building Construction</li>\n 	<li>Energy Data Analytics</li>\n 	<li>Business Case Development</li>\n 	<li>Leveraging Tax and Utility Incentives</li>\n 	<li>Energy Demand Management</li>\n 	<li>Remote Monitoring and Controls</li>\n</ol>\n-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<figure class=\"figure\">\n                        <img src=\"resources/img/4.png\" class=\"figure-img img-fluid\" alt=\"A generic square placeholder image with rounded corners in a figure.\"><figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">A caption for the above image.</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section-workshops\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h4 class=\"title\">Companies that have participated in “Energy Management Workshops”</h4>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Owen Illinois</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Pliant</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Dana</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Tenneco</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Newell</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Visteon</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Paper-Mate</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Bocar</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Nalco</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                AMF Bowling Centers</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Freedom Communications</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Griffin Wheel</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Intellitec</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Summit Christian Center</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Excel Polymers</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Pfizer</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Quebecor</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Textron</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Ralcorp</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Rexam</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Crown Cork and Seal</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Berry Plastics</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Sun Chemical</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Electromotive Diesel</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Bell Helicopter</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Greif</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Lear</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Firestone</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Pinnacle Foods</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Simmons Food</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Eaton</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Silgan Plastics</div>\n<div class=\"badge badge-pill chip\">\n                Compass Minerals</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section-experts\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h4 class=\"title\">Our Experts</h4>\n<div class=\"card shadow p-3 mb-5 bg-white rounded border border-light\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<div class=\"media\">\n                        <img class=\"mr-3 rounded-circle\" src=\"resources/img/3.jpg\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\">\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h5 class=\"mt-0\">Thomas C. Mort, BS, CEM</h5>\nPresident\nThomas Mort Consulting, LLC\n<h5>Qualification Summary:</h5>\nThomas Mort is a strong, innovative, recognized leader in the field of operational excellence and continuous improvement with more than 30 years’ experience.\n\nHe is currently President of Thomas Mort Consulting LLC based in the US and Mort International Energy Consultants based in Mexico.  He leads a team of experts matching “best available energy technologies” to cost conscious facilities.Breaking down project barriers and turning them into cost effective opportunities.\n\nHe was previously the Global Energy Director for Archer Daniels Midland Company and at Delphi Automotive Systems.  His responsibilities included developing, leading, implementing, and administrating company-wide programs focused on improving methods for managing energy usage.\n\nHe has extensive international experience and training in multiple plant systems, along with technical team leadership, motivational presentations, and global program implementation.\n\nThomas’s unique energy management workshop programs are utilized by many consultants and corporations to drive low cost high value energy reductions across large global manufacturing companies.\n<h5>Certifications, Licenses, and Recognitions:</h5>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Presenter at the World Energy Engineering Congress, 2017.</li>\n 	<li>Recognized as a “Fellow Member” of the Association of Energy Engineers 2017.</li>\n 	<li>International Energy Manager of the Year 2013, Association of Energy Engineers.</li>\n 	<li>BS In Nuclear Engineering Technology A Certified Energy Management Engineer, CEM since 1997</li>\n 	<li>Licensed Senior Reactor Operator for the Big Rock Point Nuclear Power Plant</li>\n 	<li>Inducted as a Legends in Energy by the Association of Energy Engineers in 2008</li>\n 	<li>Society of Automotive Engineers (SAE) International Environmental Excellence Awards 2001</li>\n 	<li>Society of Automotive Engineers (SAE) International Environmental Excellence Awards 2002</li>\n 	<li>Energy Manager of the Year US 1999 presented by the Energy Manager Magazine</li>\n 	<li>Elected member of the CPS Energy Citizens Advisory Committee</li>\n 	<li>Published white papers relating to metering, HVAC, compressed air, heat recovery, lighting, demand control, water conservation, and structured analysis processes.</li>\n 	<li>ISO 50001 Presentations at the World Energy Engineering Congress 2011.</li>\n 	<li>Key Speaker at multiple manufacturing and energy conferences across US and Europe.</li>\n 	<li>Key Speaker at the Academy of Science Industrial Heat Recovery Conference 2011.</li>\n 	<li>Compressed Air Best Practices Advisory Board since 2012 Active member of IECA, Industrial Energy Consumers of America.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card shadow p-3 mb-5 bg-white rounded border border-light\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<div class=\"media\">\n                        <img class=\"mr-3\" src=\"resources/img/5.png\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\">\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h5 class=\"mt-0\">Jason Bell, BS, CEM</h5>\nJason Bell has a strong background  in both manufacturing and energy management with over 18 years of practical experience.  He has led energy &amp; efficiency improvement projects throughout North America with focus on reducing costs and improving sustainability.\n\nHe has a tremendous knowledge of New York state rebate, incentive, and energy sponsored programs with a proven history of helping organizations find funding support.\n\nAs a Lean Black Belt, Jason specializes in reducing waste from within processes and involving the entire factory in maximizing solutions.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>","Imagine: Building-Green","","inherit","closed","closed","","35-revision-v1","","","2018-10-19 17:47:08","2018-10-19 17:47:08","",35,"http://savingwithenergy.local/35-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
